#. <section class="sutta" id="sn22.76"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.76:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.76:0.2"
msgid "8. Khajjanīyavagga"
msgstr "8. Itchy"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.76:0.3"
msgid "76. Arahantasutta"
msgstr "76. The Perfected Ones"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.83"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.76:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn22.76:1.2"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ."
msgstr "“Mendicants, form is impermanent."

msgctxt "sn22.76:1.3"
msgid "Yadaniccaṃ taṃ dukkhaṃ;"
msgstr "What’s impermanent is suffering."

msgctxt "sn22.76:1.4"
msgid "yaṃ dukkhaṃ tadanattā;"
msgstr "What’s suffering is not-self."

msgctxt "sn22.76:1.5"
msgid ""
"yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ "
"sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ."
msgstr ""
"And what’s not-self should be truly seen with proper understanding like this:"
" ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’"

msgctxt "sn22.76:1.6"
msgid "Vedanā …"
msgstr "Feeling …"

msgctxt "sn22.76:1.7"
msgid "saññā …"
msgstr "Perception …"

msgctxt "sn22.76:1.8"
msgid "saṅkhārā …"
msgstr "Choices …"

msgctxt "sn22.76:1.9"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ aniccaṃ."
msgstr "Consciousness is impermanent."

msgctxt "sn22.76:1.10"
msgid "Yadaniccaṃ taṃ dukkhaṃ;"
msgstr "What’s impermanent is suffering."

msgctxt "sn22.76:1.11"
msgid "yaṃ dukkhaṃ tadanattā;"
msgstr "What’s suffering is not-self."

msgctxt "sn22.76:1.12"
msgid ""
"yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ "
"sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ."
msgstr ""
"And what’s not-self should be truly seen with proper understanding like this:"
" ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.76:2.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpasmimpi nibbindati, vedanāyapi "
"… saññāyapi … saṅkhāresupi … viññāṇasmimpi nibbindati."
msgstr ""
"Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with form, "
"feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness."

msgctxt "sn22.76:2.2"
msgid ""
"Nibbindaṃ virajjati; virāgā vimuccati. Vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""
"Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re "
"freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed."

msgctxt "sn22.76:2.3"
msgid ""
"‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānāti."
msgstr ""
"They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been "
"completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any "
"state of existence.’"

msgctxt "sn22.76:2.4"
msgid ""
"Yāvatā, bhikkhave, sattāvāsā, yāvatā bhavaggaṃ, ete aggā, ete seṭṭhā "
"lokasmiṃ yadidaṃ arahanto”ti."
msgstr ""
"As far as there are abodes of sentient beings, even up until the pinnacle of "
"existence, the perfected ones are the foremost and the best.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.76:3.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "sn22.76:3.2"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā:"
msgstr "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.76:4.1"
msgid "“Sukhino vata arahanto,"
msgstr "“Oh! The perfected ones are happy."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:4.2"
msgid "taṇhā tesaṃ na vijjati;"
msgstr "Craving is not found in them,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:4.3"
msgid "Asmimāno samucchinno,"
msgstr "the conceit ‘I am’ is cut off,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:4.4"
msgid "mohajālaṃ padālitaṃ."
msgstr "and the net of delusion is shattered."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.76:5.1"
msgid "Anejaṃ te anuppattā,"
msgstr "They’ve attained stillness,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:5.2"
msgid "cittaṃ tesaṃ anāvilaṃ;"
msgstr "their minds are unclouded,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:5.3"
msgid "Loke anupalittā te,"
msgstr "nothing in the world clings to them,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:5.4"
msgid "brahmabhūtā anāsavā."
msgstr "they’ve become holy, undefiled."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.76:6.1"
msgid "Pañcakkhandhe pariññāya,"
msgstr "Completely understanding the five aggregates,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:6.2"
msgid "satta saddhammagocarā;"
msgstr "their domain is the seven good qualities."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:6.3"
msgid "Pasaṃsiyā sappurisā,"
msgstr "Those good people are praiseworthy,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:6.4"
msgid "puttā buddhassa orasā."
msgstr "the Buddha’s rightful children."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.76:7.1"
msgid "Sattaratanasampannā,"
msgstr "Endowed with the seven gems,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:7.2"
msgid "Tīsu sikkhāsu sikkhitā;"
msgstr "and trained in the three trainings,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:7.3"
msgid "Anuvicaranti mahāvīrā,"
msgstr "the great heroes live on,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:7.4"
msgid "Pahīnabhayabheravā."
msgstr "with fear and terror given up."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.76:8.1"
msgid "Dasahaṅgehi sampannā,"
msgstr "Endowed with ten factors,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:8.2"
msgid "mahānāgā samāhitā;"
msgstr "those giants have immersion."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:8.3"
msgid "Ete kho seṭṭhā lokasmiṃ,"
msgstr "These are the best in the world,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:8.4"
msgid "taṇhā tesaṃ na vijjati."
msgstr "craving is not found in them."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.76:9.1"
msgid "Asekhañāṇamuppannaṃ,"
msgstr "The master’s knowledge has arisen:"

#. <br>
#. VAR: antimoyaṃ → antimassa (mr)
msgctxt "sn22.76:9.2"
msgid "antimoyaṃ samussayo;"
msgstr "‘This bag of bones is my last.’"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:9.3"
msgid "Yo sāro brahmacariyassa,"
msgstr "They are independent of others"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:9.4"
msgid "tasmiṃ aparapaccayā."
msgstr "in the core of the spiritual path."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.84"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.76:10.1"
msgid "Vidhāsu na vikampanti,"
msgstr "Unwavering in the face of discrimination,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:10.2"
msgid "vippamuttā punabbhavā;"
msgstr "they’re freed from future lives."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:10.3"
msgid "Dantabhūmimanuppattā,"
msgstr "They’ve reached the level of the tamed,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:10.4"
msgid "te loke vijitāvino."
msgstr "in the world, they’re the winners."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.76:11.1"
msgid "Uddhaṃ tiriyaṃ apācīnaṃ,"
msgstr "Above, below, and all around,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:11.2"
msgid "nandī tesaṃ na vijjati;"
msgstr "relishing is not found in them."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:11.3"
msgid "Nadanti te sīhanādaṃ,"
msgstr "They roar their lion’s roar:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:11.4"
msgid "buddhā loke anuttarā”ti."
msgstr "‘The awakened are supreme in the world!’”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.76:11.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
